---
import { DollarSign, Gauge, Smartphone, TriangleAlert } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="w-full px-4 sm:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24 bg-bgMain brutal-border-b relative z-10">
	<div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto observe-block">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-12 gap-6">
			<div>
				<span class="text-[12px] font-mono font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">[ 01. The Problem ]</span>
				<h2 class="text-fluid-h2 leading-[0.95] font-bold uppercase flex flex-col">
					<span class="reveal-overflow"><span class="reveal-text block">Is Your Site</span></span>
					<span class="reveal-overflow"><span class="reveal-text block text-outline">A Liability?</span></span>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="stamp-item delay-200 text-[16px] md:text-[18px] font-[500] text-textSecondary border-l-4 border-black pl-4 max-w-md">
				Most local business websites are slow, outdated, or barely maintained. They quietly lose visitors, leads, and trust every day.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
			<div class="stamp-item shadow-brutal delay-100 bg-surface brutal-border p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<Gauge className="w-8 h-8 lg:w-10 lg:h-10 mb-6" />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold uppercase mb-3">Slow & Bloated</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-textSecondary font-[500]">Taking 5+ seconds to load kills your Google ranking and frustrates users.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="stamp-item shadow-brutal delay-200 bg-surface brutal-border p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<Smartphone className="w-8 h-8 lg:w-10 lg:h-10 mb-6" />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold uppercase mb-3">Mobile-Broken</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-textSecondary font-[500]">A broken mobile experience guarantees lost local searches to competitors.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="stamp-item shadow-brutal delay-300 bg-warning text-black brutal-border p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<TriangleAlert className="w-8 h-8 lg:w-10 lg:h-10 mb-6" />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold uppercase mb-3">Abandoned</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] font-[500]">Built on old WordPress plugins by a developer who vanished. Security risk.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="stamp-item shadow-brutal delay-400 bg-black text-white brutal-border p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<DollarSign className="w-8 h-8 lg:w-10 lg:h-10 mb-6" />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold uppercase mb-3">Lost Leads</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-gray-300 font-[500]">Forms silently fail, calls aren't tracked, and opportunities slip away.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
